OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FThe UK has confirmed it will send
OL,7,Fwarship HMS Dragon to Cyprus after a
OL,8,FBritish base on the island was hit by
OL,9,Fa drone.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer confirmed the UK
OL,12,Fwould be sending the ship, one of the
OL,13,FRoyal Navy's six Type 45 air defence
OL,14,Fdestroyers, after the attack on RAF
OL,15,FAkrotiri.
OL,17,FWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,18,Fcapabilities?
OL,20,FWhat is it?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
