OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FHMS Dragon is one of the most advanced
OL,7,Fwarships in the world, according to
OL,8,Fthe Royal Navy.
OL,10,FIt is one of six Type 45 air defence
OL,11,Fdestroyers, known as the Daring class,
OL,12,Fwhich were purpose-built for anti-
OL,13,Faircraft and anti-missile warfare.
OL,15,FInstantly recognisable by the large
OL,16,Fred Welsh Dragon on her bow, HMS
OL,17,FDragon is manned by more than 200
OL,18,Fpersonnel and is currently based in
OL,19,FPortsmouth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
