PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772589792
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FDespite the name 'destroyer', the ship
OL,7,Fis built for a range of missions from
OL,8,Fcombating pirates and defending
OL,9,Fagainst air attacks, to delivering
OL,10,Fhumanitarian aid.
OL,12,FWhat capabilities does it have?
OL,14,FAll six of the UK's Type 45 destroyers
OL,15,Ffeature a missile system known as Sea
OL,16,FViper, which is "designed to track,
OL,17,Ftarget and destroy a variety of high-
OL,18,Flevel air threats", including cruise
OL,19,Fmissiles, fighter jets and drones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
