OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772589792
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FAccording to the Royal Navy, it can
OL,7,Flaunch eight missiles in under ten
OL,8,Fseconds and simultaneously guide up to
OL,9,F16, hitting targets with precision
OL,10,Ffrom over 70 miles away.
OL,12,FIts multifunctional radar can detect
OL,13,Fair and surface targets from a
OL,14,Fdistance of 250 miles and is capable
OL,15,Fof tracking hundreds of targets
OL,16,Fsimultaneously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
