PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772589792
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Dragon and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FAs well as two Phalanx 20mm close-in
OL,7,Fweapons systems, the ships have an
OL,8,Farray of weaponry, including the BAE
OL,9,FSystems 4.5-inch Mark 8 Mode 1, two
OL,10,F30mm DSM Mark 2s, two 7.62mm miniguns
OL,11,Fand up to six FN MAG general purpose
OL,12,Fmachine guns.
OL,14,FThe Type 45 destroyers also feature a
OL,15,Fflight deck and hangar to support the
OL,16,Foperation of a single Merlin
OL,17,Fhelicopter, which can be used for
OL,18,F"round-the-clock maritime patrol",
OL,19,Foffensive attacks and search and
OL,20,Frescue missions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
